qwen2.5:7b.text:
The bug in your code is that the condition `num % 2 === 1` is incorrect for determining if a number is even. For a number to be even, the remainder when divided by 2 should be 0. Here is the corrected code:

```javascript
// Comprueba si el número es par
function isEven(num) {
    return num % 2 === 0;  // Corrección aquí
}
```

This function will now correctly return `true` for even numbers and `false` for odd numbers.

